            <td colspan="1">$a - Original cataloging agency (NR)<br>$b - Language of cataloging (NR)<br>$c - Transcribing agency (NR)<br>$d - Modifying agency (R)<br></td>
            <td colspan="1">$e - Description conventions (R)<br>$f - Subject heading/thesaurus conventions (NR)<br>$6 - Linkage (NR)<br>$8 - Field link and sequence number (R)<br></td>
