         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$b - Language of cataloging</strong> <em></em><div class="description">MARC code for the language of the catalog for which the record is intended. Code
                              from: <em><a href="http://www.loc.gov/marc/languages/">MARC Code List for Languages</a></em>.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$c - Transcribing agency</strong> <em></em><div class="description">MARC code or the name of the organization that transcribed the record into
                              machine-readable form.
